# Unit Tests Directory

Place unit test files here following the naming convention:
- `*.test.ts` for TypeScript tests
- `*.spec.ts` for specification-style tests

Example structure:
```
tests/unit/
  domain/
    identity/
      user.entity.test.ts
      auth.service.test.ts
    messaging/
      message.entity.test.ts
      message.service.test.ts
    presence/
      presence.service.test.ts
  lib/
    socket/
      connection.handler.test.ts
      message.handler.test.ts
    redis/
      cache.service.test.ts
  components/
    chat/
      MessageInput.test.tsx
      MessageList.test.tsx
  hooks/
    useSocket.test.ts
    useMessages.test.ts
```
